      special damages arising from your use of the site or reliance on
      information found here, including but not limited to underpayment or
      overpayment of tax, penalties, or interest.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Third-party links and ads</h2>
    <p>
      The site contains links to third-party websites and serves
      advertisements through Google AdSense. We do not endorse and are not
      responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of any third-party
